org.sakaiproject.user.api

Interface UserFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseUserDirectoryService, DbUserService

    public interface UserFactory

    UserFactory is an interface for facility to create User objects consistent with the current UserDirectoryService implementation. This is useful when a provider is wanting to create user objects to be returned from a ExternalUserSearchUDP.searchExternalUsers(String, int, int, UserFactory) call.
